title: 100,000 Hi-Res Images of Classic and Surrealist Paintings
description:
This is a image collection of classic and surrealist paintings. There are 100,000 high resolution images. In this archive there is no sorting. The files are all in a single folder and named to their md5 checksums to prevent duplicates.

The purpose is to make this vast collection accessible to the wallpaper rotation system and screensavers included with OSX that require a single folder of images.

You can be exposed to fine art passively with this archive using those features.
